[I] The fast and easy UI Toolkit

[T] Slint (formerly known as The SixtyFPS project) is a toolkit to
[T] efficiently develop fluid graphical user interfaces for any
[T] display: embedded devices and desktop applications. We support
[T] multiple programming languages, such as Rust, C++, and JavaScript.

[U] https://slint-ui.com/

[A] SixtyFPS GmbH
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] base/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 1.16.0

[CV-FLAGS] NO-PREFIX
[D] 3b484f5e3f06fbebffa0376ecc2f2e77c14700ddcaca9c11147087e5 slint-ui-1.16.0.tar.gz https://github.com/slint-ui/slint/archive/v1.16.0/

